OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet morning as rain spreads
OL,6,Facross the region, locally heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Rain turning lighter and
OL,8,Fpatchier in the afternoon but
OL,9,Fremaining widely cloudy with hill and
OL,10,Fcoastal fog at times. Feeling muggy
OL,11,Fdespite being windy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy into the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight with further
OL,15,Foutbreaks of light rain and drizzle,
OL,16,Fmostly over the hills. Remaining
OL,17,Fwidely breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
