OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FLargely cloudy and breezy on
OL,6,FFriday with patchy rain or drizzle,
OL,7,Fparticularly over the hills and moors.
OL,8,FSome brighter or sunnier spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping during the afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling warmer than recently.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFurther
OL,13,Fshowers possible on Saturday.
OL,14,FOtherwise becoming increasingly
OL,15,Fsettled on Sunday with drier and
OL,16,Fwarmer conditions developing. Similar
OL,17,Fon Monday perhaps feeling very warm in
OL,18,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
